The application framework uses the following directories.

app		- application specific files
	cfg					- configuration files
	controllers			- class definitions for all controllers
	forms				- class definitions for all forms
	forms/json			- JSON configuration files for each form
	lib					- application-specific libraries
	models				- class definitions for all database models
	views				- all application views
	views/<controller>	- controller specific views

lib		- framework library files

public	- Internet facing files
	css			- CSS files
	js			- JavaScript files
	js/pp		- JavaScript files (post-processed)
	img			- image files

tmp		- temporary files
	cache		- cache files
	logs		- log files
	sessions	- session data files
